Clean, hygienic, affordable karaoke St heartland spot. Thank God it's accessible and affordable.
Join the membership has offset benefits.
You can openly bring in food and drinks, no need to smuggle. Lol..
Can buy their cholled drinks at $ 1 each.

Convenient neighbourhood place.
Paid $19+ for peak hour.
2 of us, room is a little hot but overall experience is great (:

On my day of visit the counter lady was professional, there was a rude man kept trying to cut our conversion to extend his hour. This lady finished my registration first despite the multiple interruption (:
Great place to gather with friends, one of the more affordable karaoke places. Would recommend to call in before you go over, they are always fully booked.
Happy with the Audio and video system, may not be good for others. I am happy with the atmosphere. And I have fun with my friends.

Nice place for ktv teo heng. Cc does feel a bit old but place is kept very well and clean.

4pax room quite small. I feel its more for 3pax. 4 of us adults sat on the sofa and our arms were kissing. Lol
